rows.label: tlk42360111_05_msg0001
rows.name:
While sailing, I saw the shadow
of a sunken ship that had sunk
into the Cloud Sea, mo!

rows.label: tlk42360111_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Just one look, and I felt a jolt
of treasure and adventure, mo!

rows.label: tlk42360111_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I think there's so much treasure
that you could explore forever and
not find it all, mo! Probably!

rows.label: tlk42360111_05_msg0004
rows.name:
But, but... Kajiji is too busy piloting
Goldmund to go exploring, mo.

rows.label: tlk42360111_05_msg0005
rows.name:
I was hoping you'd bite,
mo! We'll split the treasure
with Kajiji, mo!!
